name: Look In A Window - Just Watching Ep.1
description:
There we are with the first episode of my new series!
The "Office" episode! This was the first idea I had, during my creative block, casually, in an office.

---
A small series born from the idea that looking through a window could be endless, and endless.

Prepare to have a glance, Inside!

This series was made in a heavy period of creative block, as a way to take my creative side breath, and is based around the concept of creating catching, 3d art, not-so-real endless animations!
This series will be the way I'll go through my creative block period, and I hope you all come on board!
